{"tid":1725830,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《海賊王結束》編輯承認5年內結局：「和之國篇好關鍵，一定要睇！」","createTime":"2019-11-16T01:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T03:33:34.000Z","uid":43785,"like":11,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"e65b22e7f587f35c09c63a2ba7f6b922ad0a5656","tid":1725830,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:39:32.000Z","msg":"《海賊王》編輯承認5年內結局：「和之國篇好關鍵，一定要睇！」<br />\n<br />\n《One Piece》海賊王最新章連載「和之國篇」近半年，太多回憶、節奏遲緩令投訴不絕，《OP》責任編輯内藤拓真在一段訪問中再次確定作品會在5年內完結，且建議大家不要錯過「和之國篇」，因為關鍵劇情即將出現！<br />\n<br />\n近日《鬼滅之刃》單行本銷量超前《One Piece》，令人有種JUMP又進入交接期的預感。上個月我們曾報導過尾田榮一郎接受訪問時發放「One Piece 將在5年內完結」的爆炸性消息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xzfOs4x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxzfOs4x.jpg&h=9fea02a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但按照集英社傳統，《週刊少年Jump》編輯部那會輕易放過尾田呢？一定不給他完結吧？但可能近年Jump的方針也與時並進不再拖戲；角色死得好快、故事推進更快，5年內完畢的消息，近日竟在日本網頁「Oricon」的《One Piece》電影版宣傳訪問中，由集英社《週刊少年Jump》的《海賊王》責任編輯内藤拓真再度確認屬實！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9viMeKO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9viMeKO.jpg&h=79bc2cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n訪問是關於已上映電影《ONE PIECE STAMPEDE》的，劇中海賊王葛魯&middot;D&middot;羅渣大秘寶所在地終有眉目，指向最終島「LAUGH TALE」（拉夫德鲁）的永久指針都也現身；而既然電影亦開始入最終直路，漫畫也不能再拖拖拉拉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvygBYK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvygBYK.jpg&h=49a956fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyQuWYP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyQuWYP.jpg&h=538e0778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">前往最終之島的永久指針已經出現</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbnX5Sa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbnX5Sa.jpg&h=245155cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HsLnxxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsLnxxb.jpg&h=2b80097d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">海賊王羅渣埋下的one piece即將揭盅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n究竟是不是5年就完？<br />\n<br />\n「我自己不這樣認為，我覺得還有很多空間寫下去，但既然尾田主意已決，就5年內完結它吧！」内藤編輯認為，以和之國篇的節奏和密度，5年內大結局是可行的，不過尾田老師仍然有很多想法，仍有很多島嶼想畫，所以接下來《One Piece》將已極之高的密度繪畫下去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wp4zoED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwp4zoED.jpg&h=72740377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">只要在google搜尋和之國篇，第一個關鍵字就是悶</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bS8cUMh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbS8cUMh.jpg&h=24b00672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">尾田榮一郎拖戲，卓洛和山自已經五年沒有同場。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFhxajD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFhxajD.jpg&h=8deaea8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">網上有人話和之國比魚人島到更悶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和之國篇會唔會太多回憶殺？<br />\n<br />\n本篇將回憶當年葛魯&middot;D&middot;羅渣藏寶的經過，也會寫新角色「光月おでん」（光月關東煮）的秘密、跟路飛一行人有什麼關連，細節雖然不能講，但可以肯定說，和之國篇正是整套作品的核心劇情，也會解釋什麼是「One Piece」！所以絕不能錯過。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hk38s6B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHk38s6B.jpg&h=1497341c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">光月禦田原來跟one piece有莫大關係</span></span><br />\n<br />\n棄了書的朋友也一定要回歸！<br />\n<br />\n内藤編輯雖沒有直接回應連載最新作「和之國篇」被指推進有點遲緩的問題，但卻提到：「和之國篇跟最終結局之間有重大的關連，而高潮亦會即將出現。所以無論是從未買過《One Piece》漫畫，又或是早已棄書的fans，都請一定要從91期單行本（和之國篇）開始／回歸。<br />\n<br />\n相關訪問之日本網頁「Oricon News Japan」連結<br />\n<br />\n雖說《鬼滅之刃》單行本銷售首次超越OP，但尾田作為現在Jump系三甲級大師，對他而言仍絕對未談不上有「壓力」，但似乎從好的方向帶給《OP》製作單位一種：「開始要來個了結啦」的覺悟，我們就拭目以待《One Piece》來個最精彩的結尾吧。<br />\n<br />\n終於唔拖戲？？？<br />\n明哥走甩左？？？"},{"pid":"d996bb35f25fa76d51155ea3136acf4e9b25aa08","tid":1725830,"uid":69269,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:40:09.000Z","msg":"Good morning sir"},{"pid":"6f32aad6cc080e6be4723d71a9f661f43037ea98","tid":1725830,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:40:13.000Z","msg":"Hi sir"},{"pid":"8c37150214a378dcf380dc5d62325bb6a4231d4a","tid":1725830,"uid":98603,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:40:24.000Z","msg":"你點知的"},{"pid":"8111fb2bd69ba294723bcc1c49c6600a564729ad","tid":1725830,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:40:38.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca4be6761da7d995d654940b44b23dc75a51f59","tid":1725830,"uid":190406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:40:39.000Z","msg":"Sir"},{"pid":"d944084f5117671b4444693466ccce23385510c3","tid":1725830,"uid":133377,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:40:45.000Z","msg":"呀sir唔該講啲有建設性啲既野得唔得"},{"pid":"98f2ad31d3565eeb01cf781a1c5850b81fbfb55b","tid":1725830,"uid":43785,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"d944084f5117671b4444693466ccce23385510c3","tid":1725830,"uid":133377,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:40:45.000Z","msg":"呀sir唔該講啲有建設性啲既野得唔得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:41:05.000Z","msg":"動漫台呀大佬"},{"pid":"76295bb3b63f153680c6da2ed4d9f02dcd73be19","tid":1725830,"uid":209900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:41:10.000Z","msg":"Good morning sir"},{"pid":"09f558b906de94e432d6d0316ef8ed57dff683be","tid":1725830,"uid":246156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"yes sir"},{"pid":"ec23f9f9113d614e7bd90ac6ce820edce7f56005","tid":1725830,"uid":239709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":